# 2026-03-10 23:23:34.941113
+Completely redesign index.html to match the look and feel of vyorawellness.com. Keep all the Revive Longevity content (brand name, top 10 peptides, etc.) but adopt this design style:
+
+DESIGN SYSTEM (inspired by vyorawellness.com):
+- Background: warm cream/off-white (#F5F2E9 and #EBE8DD)
+- Primary dark color: deep teal/charcoal (#253031)
+- Accent: muted sage green or warm teal (#778B8B)
+- Text: dark charcoal on light backgrounds
+- Font: Use 'DM Sans' or 'Instrument Sans' from Google Fonts (closest free alternative to Suisse Intl)
+- Overall feel: clean, minimal, light, airy, premium wellness clinic — NOT dark/techy
+
+LAYOUT CHANGES:
+- Hero: large clean headline, light background, soft imagery placeholder, quiz/CTA button in warm teal
+- Navigation: minimal, light background, logo left, links right
+- Peptide cards: light cards with soft borders, warm background, subtle hover shadows
+- Stats bar: clean horizontal stats strip (members, satisfaction rate, etc.)
+- Testimonials section: add 3 fake testimonials with names, age, location
+- How It Works: clean 3-step with numbered circles in teal
+- FAQ: clean accordion, light styling
+- Footer: dark teal background (#253031) with cream text
+
+FEEL: Think premium wellness spa meets modern medical clinic. Warm, trustworthy, approachable. Like vyorawellness.com but for peptide longevity therapy.

